islike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T17:38:39.000Z","msg":"行山都發現呢樣野<br />\n可能因為打風<br />\n水土流失<br />\n要起新巢"},{"pid":"e31f2d335daa234366a8daf72dd45f891e8e2734","tid":842922,"uid":12264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T17:39:14.000Z","msg":"呢樣真，真係多左好多，仲要之前明明完唔見有"},{"pid":"482466ccdf102d6b1ba2321ef9b526d20ec2c73b","tid":842922,"uid":117232,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T17:40:51.000Z","msg":"見到呢個post 特登upload 自己一年前屋企蟻災既片<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Ngv-cH2oTgY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FNgv-cH2oTgY&d=NFQt358hQrnvUw6KPkXYQIzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=0c3f7042\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Ngv-cH2oTgY</a><br />\n（慎入）<br />\n果陣屋企放個面包係飯枱，唔夠十分鐘就有螞蟻爬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，<br />\n<br />\n之後嚴重到掉食物殘渣係垃圾桶，都引一大堆螞蟻<br />\n<br />\n我果陣專登唔理佢，半個鐘後成條蟻路出左黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> （諗返起都身痕）<br />\n我跟住條蟻路，搵到螞蟻全部都係廁所細洞出黎，即刻用殺蟲水噴洞，再觀察螞蟻會點走，之後連封幾個細洞，再留意所以螞蟻不停係細洞附近四圍行，好似迷路咁，呢個時候可以停手。<br />\n第二日發覺螞蟻少左好多，一星期後直頭無哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16ac5ce521c634e8ba9a4d265e629ac3fb29fde2","tid":842922,"uid":163262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b446bfef43750a35ea7f75e190256c1bbb6a3f5d","tid":842922,"uid":22349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"adc6bda54326bc73850e1e7ca9edfb3a31e20b0c","tid":842922,"uid":163262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T17:27:25.000Z","msg":"我屋企都係 近呢幾個月搵到幾個蟻竇<br />\n個感覺好似比異形入侵屋企咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n依家買咗啲蟻粉同白英泥<br />\n毒撚死哂佢班仆街再封番住個窿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T17:34:09.000Z","msg":"點搵到蟻竇 主動出擊"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T17:42:20.000Z","msg":"啲蟻通常下就最活躍<br />\n之後就搵下邊度最多蟻 通常望望下就會搵到條路<br />\n順住條路就會搵到個竇<br />\n或者我自己有時會望住一隻蟻爬去邊<br />\n通常望望下就會出現多兩三隻"},{"pid":"9f6a3b60fc2ea79a87b411a673c965e66491ea0b","tid":842922,"uid":22349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T18:28:48.000Z","msg":"屋企啲蟻多到爬上眼鏡，backpack, 同爬上手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}